data.name: Term Deposit
data.description: Earn great returns with an IMB Term Deposit. An IMB Term Deposit offers competitive returns for investment terms from 1 month up to 5 years for amounts of $1,000 or more. Term Deposits are a secure way to grow your savings for the future!

features.additionalInfo: Internet Banking and Mobile Banking App.
IMB boasts an extensive branch network throughout the Illawarra, Sydney, NSW South Coast, the ACT and Melbourne.
IMB's Phone Banking Service gives you 24 hour access to your accounts from any touchphone.
IMB consultants are available Monday to Friday 8am - 8pm and Saturday 9am - 4pm
